{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Call for review of US military presence on UK territory.",
        "additional_details": "Review of US military presence on UK territory in light of increasing concerns about consistency and reliability of current leadership. We urge the government to establish clear conditions governing continued presence of US forces, ensure operational transparency, and allow for the suspension or withdrawal of access.\r\n\r\nDevelop and implement a framework that enables the reduction or removal of US military presence on UK soil if determined that such presence no longer aligns with our interests.",
        "background": "Review US military presence on UK sovereign territory.\r\n\r\nRecent rhetoric and policy positions raise questions about the US commitment to UK, NATO, its approach to allied co-operation, and potential impact on our economic and strategic interests.",
